            </p>
          </div>
          <p class='text-xs font-light text-darkestGrey dark:text-grey mt-1'>
          517 pages <span class="toggle-edition-info-link" data-book-id=c9ca5bdd-30da-48ad-a0c9-3c9ac03a297a><span class="text-darkerGrey dark:text-lightGrey"> • </span> <span class="underline decoration-darkerGrey dark:decoration-lightgrey cursor-pointer hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500 hover:decoration-cyan-700 dark:hover:decoration-cyan-500">first pub 2023</span></span>  (<a class="browse-editions-link text-xs text-darkestGrey dark:text-grey cursor-pointer font-light hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500 underline decoration-darkerGrey dark:decoration-lightGrey hover:decoration-cyan-700 dark:hover:decoration-cyan-500 mt-1 pb-1" href="/books/c9ca5bdd-30da-48ad-a0c9-3c9ac03a297a/editions">editions</a>) 
                    </p>
          <div class="hidden edition-info mt-3" data-book-id=c9ca5bdd-30da-48ad-a0c9-3c9ac03a297a>
            <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-semibold">ISBN/UID:</span>  9781649374042</p>
